   Contact Us:

   For additional information concerning the Job Openings and Labor
   Turnover Survey (JOLTS), contact a JOLTS staff member at:
     * Email address: JOLTSInfo@bls.gov
     * Telephone number: (202) 691-5870
     * Fax number: (202) 691-6645
     * Postal address:
       Office of Employment and Unemployment Statistics
       Job Openings and Labor Turnover Survey
       Suite 4840
       2 Massachusetts Avenue, NE
       Washington, DC 20212-0001

   Survey participants needing assistance completing their monthly report,
   call 1-800-341-4620.

